<TEXT>
   A high school boy and girl performed a
sex act in a classroom in front of at least a dozen students,
authorities said.
   The students, both 16 and ninth-graders at Chattanooga High
School, were charged Tuesday with agreeing to perform a sex act for
money, police said.
