<HEAD>Aide: Marcos Rehospitalized For ``Routine Checkup''</HEAD>
<DATELINE>HONOLULU (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Deposed Philippine President Ferdinand Marcos
returned to the hospital for an hour Wednesday and underwent
follow-up tests for an ailment that put him in the the hospital
last week, a Marcos spokesman said.
   ``It was nothing more than a routine checkup,'' said Gemmo
